Package com.worklight.jsonstore.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JSONStoreAddOptions
    Options that are used to modify the add operation in JSONStoreCollection.
    JSONStoreChangeOptions
    Options that are used to modify the change operation in JSONStoreCollection.
    JSONStoreCollection
    This class represents a single JSONStore collection.
    JSONStoreCountOptions
    Options that are used to modify the count operation in JSONStoreCollection.
    JSONStoreFileInfo
    Represents information about a JSONStore database file.
    JSONStoreFindOptions
    Options that are used to modify the find operation in JSONStoreCollection.
    JSONStoreInitOptions
    Options that are used to modify the init operation in WLJSONStore.
    JSONStoreQueryPart
    Represents a group of operations that are joined with an AND.
    JSONStoreQueryParts
    Represents a group of query parts that are joined with an OR statement.
    JSONStoreRemoveOptions
    Options that are used to modify the remove operation in JSONStoreCollection.
    JSONStoreReplaceOptions
    Options that are used to modify the replace operation in JSONStoreCollection.
    WLJSONStore
    This class is the public JSONStore API for native Android applications.
